Package: smallcount
Type: Package
Title: Methods for Small Counts Stored in a Sparse Matrix 
Version: 0.1.2
Author: Rafael A. Irizarry
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: Matrix, RSpectra, methods, inline, RcppArmadillo, Rcpp
Suggests: scuttle, knitr, rmarkdown, bench
Maintainer: Rafael A. Irizarry <rafael_irizarry@dfci.harvard.edu>
Description: Functions for performing common tasks in genomics data analysis of small counts that are mostly zeros such as data generated by current single cell technologies.
